{
  "stem": "9878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I understand that a day, two days later, when the Russians came in, they disarmed all the Polish soldiers, and they took them-- so especially, they took a lot of-- in the PWs, and especially captains and officers.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which, it happened after that, that the famous and the tragic act in, in, in Katyn, Katyn, Russia, that-- and unfortunately, because all the people were mobilized in Poland to fight against the, the, the Germans, the majority of the officers in the Polish Army happened to be Jewish professionals-- doctors, lawyers, dentists.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the result was that in Katyn, about 88% of the officers that the Russians killed were Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there were-- they were-- they were inducted into the army during the war, taken from their offices.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were in the intelligentsia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were the professionals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The, the, the-- this was a tragic-- a tragic case that happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did the Russian occupation affect your schooling?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russian occupation affected our schooling in a way that we had to stop short any, any religious education.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I signed up to high school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Russian, it's called [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very young then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[RUSSIAN] means 10-year school-- high school and public school together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had to go and study general studies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It means everything in Russian, nothing Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Jewish schools right way closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The yeshivas, they closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They curtailed the, the, the Jewish people going to the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the Jewish people had to-- had to pray Saturdays in their own-- in their own houses, with people getting together and praying.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was not such to do-- they did only-- not only to the Jewish people, they could tell the people going to the churches, too.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were trying to indoctrinate the people against their religion.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
